          br
          .inline.fields
            label(for='wouldRead', name='wouldRead') 
            .field
              .ui.checkbox
                input(type='checkbox')
                label(for='wouldRead', tabindex='0') I hid the advertisement from my timeline.
        .ui.form
          .inline.fields
            label(for='checkSource', name='checkSource') 
            .field
              .ui.checkbox
                input(type='checkbox')
                label(for='checkSource', tabindex='0') I reported the advertisement to the website.
        .ui.form
          .inline.fields
            label(for='corroboration', name='corroboration') 
